# Python env / caches
.venv*/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Datasets — NEVER pushed. Huge, and not ours to redistribute (PodcastFillers,
# Apple SEP-28k, your own recordings all live under data/).
data/
data-set/
# Apple SEP-28k: the clone + its downloaded audio (32 GB) + its python env.
